<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(م)</span> عبد الله بن علي بن حميد: العرب ٩/ ٦٣<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
